Epidemiology
Source of the outbreak(s) or origin of infection: unknown or inconclusive

Control measures
Measures applied: movement control inside the country; quarantine; surveillance within containment and/or protection zone; modified stamping out; no vaccination; no treatment of affected animals.
Measures to be applied: no other measures

Diagnostic test results
Laboratory name and type /
All-Russian Research Institute for Animal Health (FGBI-ARRIAH) (regional reference laboratory)
